        "subject": "LU-19772 build: Improve o2iblnd path detection",
        "message": "LU-19772 build: Improve o2iblnd path detection\n\nlustre-lnet.m4 provides a unified way to detect o2iblnd\npath but it cannot retrieve o2iblnd path in some cases (e.g\nmlnx-ofa_kernel-source and mlnx-ofa_kernel-dksm) so improve\nit by adding a default path.\n\nLustre-change: https://review.whamcloud.com/63310\nLustre-commit: 6c93398e6e3da6d751f4cbe6e1a42f528114e221\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial nettype=o2ib\nSigned-off-by: Xiao Yang <xyang@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I40ee29d4e701da7e46f2248a3ed487a37be87ee2\n"
      },
